parts.text: *Ach, mein liebling Heavy!*  Zat is a *tragedy*, ja?  But a *fascinating* one!  So many possibilities!  Perhaps a stray rocket?  Or maybeâ€¦ *a sudden and unexpected heart failure*?  Zat would be... *exciting* to investigate!  Perhaps I could even perform an autopsy!  *Oooooh, the possibilities!*  But alas, he is *dead*, and I must... *improve* him further.  He will be back, and even *better* than before, jawohl!
